			"relation": "elab-aspect"
		},
		{
			"id": 3,
			"parent": 2,
			"text": "Practical applications of this research can be framed in the context of second language learning . <S>\r",
			"relation": "elab-addition"
		},
		{
			"id": 4,
			"parent": 3,
			"text": "The type of translation assistance system under investigation here encourages language learners to write in their target language \r",
